09:36.840 --> 09:48.240
through a place that I couldn't even find on the map. It was a little village,
which, where there was a horse pulling a wagon and no overhead electrical lines

09:48.240 --> 09:56.520
in sight. It was almost as if I had driven back through time into the 19th
century. There were log buildings.

10:00.480 --> 10:07.460
