which probably answers this in a way, but I guess your relation to science

25:19.420 --> 25:31.560
fiction, if I can put it that way. Do you see yourself in it simply as a field
where you can most conveniently earn a living, Do you have some sort of a

25:31.560 --> 25:39.940
mission or a crusade to bring things to people's attention? Some people, like
